==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Outray
<hw>Out*ray"</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To spread out in array.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>And now they <qex>outray</qex> to your fleet.</q>
<rj><qau>Chapman.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

